<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Vault PKI Demo - Phase 2</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            min-height: 100vh;
            color: white;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(31, 38, 135, 0.37);
        }
        .logo {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .vault-logo {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background: #000;
            border-radius: 10px;
            display: inline-block;
            color: #FFD814;
            font-weight: bold;
            line-height: 80px;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0 40px;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }
        .status-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .status-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .status-icon {
            font-size: 2em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .demo-info {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .command-box {
            background: #2d3748;
            color: #e2e8f0;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            margin: 10px 0;
            overflow-x: auto;
        }
        .success { color: #48bb78; }
        .warning { color: #ed8936; }
        .info { color: #4299e1; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">
            <div class="vault-logo">VAULT</div>
        </div>
        
        <h1>🔐 Vault PKI Demo - Phase 2</h1>
        
        <div class="demo-info">
            <h2>🚀 Automated PKI Infrastructure</h2>
            <p><strong>Demo Server:</strong> {{ demo_hostname }}.{{ app_domain }}</p>
            <p><strong>SSL Domain:</strong> {{ demo_domain }}</p>
            <p><strong>Vault Address:</strong> {{ vault_addr }}</p>
            <p><strong>PKI Engine:</strong> {{ vault_pki_path }}</p>
            <p><strong>Current Time:</strong> <span id="current-time"></span></p>
        </div>

        <div class="status-grid">
            <div class="status-card">
                <div class="status-icon">🔑</div>
                <h3>Vault Agent</h3>
                <p class="success">✅ Auto-authenticated via AWS EC2</p>
                <p>Automatic token renewal active</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="status-card">
                <div class="status-icon">🔒</div>
                <h3>SSL Certificate</h3>
                <p class="success">✅ Auto-issued from Vault PKI</p>
                <p>TTL: {{ cert_max_ttl_h }} hours</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="status-card">
                <div class="status-icon">🔄</div>
                <h3>Auto-Renewal</h3>
                <p class="success">✅ Certificate monitoring active</p>
                <p>Apache auto-restart on cert update</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="status-card">
                <div class="status-icon">🌐</div>
                <h3>DNS Resolution</h3>
                <p class="info">Route53 A record configured</p>
                <p>{{ demo_hostname }}.{{ app_domain }}</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="demo-info">
            <h3>🔧 Manual Certificate Renewal</h3>
            <p>You can manually renew the SSL certificate using:</p>
            <div class="command-box">
sudo /usr/local/bin/renew-ssl-cert.sh
            </div>
            
            <h3>📊 Check Certificate Status</h3>
            <div class="command-box">
# View current certificate details
openssl x509 -in /etc/httpd/ssl/server.crt -text -noout

# Check certificate expiration
openssl x509 -in /etc/httpd/ssl/server.crt -dates -noout
            </div>

            <h3>🔍 Vault Agent Status</h3>
            <div class="command-box">
# Check Vault Agent service status
sudo systemctl status vault-agent

# View Vault Agent logs
sudo journalctl -u vault-agent -f
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="demo-info">
            <h3>🎯 Demo Features Demonstrated</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>✅ AWS EC2 instance metadata authentication</li>
                <li>✅ Vault Agent auto-login and token management</li>
                <li>✅ Automatic SSL certificate issuance from Vault PKI</li>
                <li>✅ Certificate auto-renewal with Apache restart</li>
                <li>✅ Route53 DNS integration</li>
                <li>✅ Systemd service management</li>
                <li>✅ File-based certificate monitoring</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function updateTime() {
            document.getElementById('current-time').textContent = new Date().toISOString();
        }
        updateTime();
        setInterval(updateTime, 1000);
    </script>
</body>
</html>
